This is the example to postprocess committee properties

make sure you install lammps(mpi or serial), i-pi and ASE.
for ase, just `pip install ase`

1. generate committee data
 1.1 cd 01generate-data
 1.2 ./run.sh to produce committee md simulation with two potentials

2. extract the values of potentials from .extra file
 2.1 cd  02extract-data
 2.2 ln -s ../01generate-data/simulation.extra_0 .
 2.3 ./extract.sh
 2.4 see the content of extract.sh for details

3. make radial distribution function from xyz file
 3.1 cd 03make-rdf
 3.2 ln -s ../1generate-data/simulation.pos_0.xyz
 3.3 python xyz2rdflist.py

4. reweight the rdf from the committee run
 4.1 cd 04reweight
 4.2 ./collect
 4.3 python run.py
 4.4 see the content of NOTE for details

 
